{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"padding_top":28,"padding_bottom":28}},"rich_text_7WegwH":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_LhjXYM":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"ÜBER PINKYPACT","heading_size":"h1"}}},"block_order":["heading_LhjXYM"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","color_scheme":"","full_width":true,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0}},"image_with_text_rcfFTU":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_ERqzWP":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"HEY","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_UDnxVW":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>ich bin Laura, die Gründerin von PINKYPACT - die beste Maniküre der Welt 💖<br\/>Ich habe die Marke mit dem Ziel gegründet, dir eine schnelle, einfache und Nagel schonende Maniküre anzubieten, die lange hält und alles mitmacht. Einfach: Aufkleben, Abfeilen, Aushärten - Fertig!<\/p><p>Der Name \"PINKYPACT\" leitet sich vom “Pinky Promise” (kleiner Finger Schwur) ab, und ich verspreche dir damit, dass ich dir immer die besten Produkte anbiete. Wenn du bei mir bestellst, schließt du mit mir den PINKYPACT 💖 <\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["heading_ERqzWP","text_UDnxVW"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Kopie_von_Foto_Laura_2.png","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","image_behavior":"none","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"image_with_text_iLjKwr":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_VQr6CJ":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"WARUM PINKYPACT?","heading_size":"h1"}},"text_tjHFft":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Ich weiß, wie wichtig es ist, dass deine Nägel gut aussehen und sich gleichzeitig gesund anfühlen. Denn Nägel haben einen positiven Einfluss auf das Mindset, die Stimmung und das Selbstbewusstsein. Ich glaube, dass jeder es verdient, sich gut zu fühlen. Deshalb habe ich die PINKYPACT UV Gel Folien entwickelt, die eine Maniküre ermöglichen, die einfach, schnell und sanft zu deinen Nägeln ist. Du kannst zwischen vielen tollen Farben und Designs auswählen. <\/p><p>Hier unterstützt du ein kleines Startup. Bei Fragen oder Problemen kannst du dich jederzeit an mich wenden.<br\/><br\/>Einige Gründe, warum PINKYPACT die beste Wahl für deine DIY Maniküre ist:<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["heading_VQr6CJ","text_tjHFft"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Foto_Laura_2.png","height":"adapt","desktop_image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"","image_behavior":"none","mobile_content_alignment":"left","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"multicolumn_UkE9Pr":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"column_mxkkid":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"<strong>100+<\/strong>","text":"<p>FARBEN<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_4LcgNr":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"<strong>10+<\/strong>","text":"<p>Länder<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_RkbNLw":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"<strong>90D<\/strong>","text":"<p>Rückgaberecht<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_6VMrGd":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"<strong>5000+<\/strong>","text":"<p>Zufriedene Kunden<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_Uy9aWj":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"90%","text":"<p>bleiben PINKYPACT treu<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["column_mxkkid","column_4LcgNr","column_RkbNLw","column_6VMrGd","column_Uy9aWj"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_size":"h1","image_width":"full","image_ratio":"adapt","columns_desktop":5,"column_alignment":"left","background_style":"primary","button_label":"","button_link":"","color_scheme":"scheme-81385bd2-db28-4181-9d14-b26e70fc9e84",